title: Sticky Pest Traps, Mehani 12 Pack Sticky Glue Boards, Large Extra Strong Sticky Pads, Efficient Foldable Sticky Traps Boards, Glue Boards for Multiple Insects in Indoor Outdoor Garage Kitchen Garden
features: Upgraded Pest Trap Boards - Mehani pest sticky pad traps are made of special glue which is strongly adhesive and evenly distributed, have no chemicals, and are safe for humans and pets. The reinforced sticky cardboard ensures these pad traps stay intact, even if the pests struggle, they can not escape.

Easy to Set up and Easy to Clean - The sticky pads trap is convenient and hassle-free, just put some baits on the glue traps then place them where pests are observed frequently, once the pest is trapped, the sticky surface does not allow them to escape, we can easily throw them along with cardboard. Recommend baits: such as peanuts, bread crumbs, fruits, sugar, etc.

Various Ways of Use - Mehani extra strong sticky glue boards can be easily folded into various shapes. You can lay them flat or fold them into an "一“ shape, "90°" shape, "U" shape, and "口" shape to target specific areas where pests frequently appear. It can avoid being touched by children or pets and be used in multiple terrains and multiple scenes, especially suitable for narrow spaces.

Wide Range of Applications - Mehani pest sticky boards have a wide range of applications. The sticky board traps are perfect for indoor and outdoor, such as for kitchens, gardens, restaurants, bars, garages, basements, storage rooms, and more. The sticky traps also effectively deal with various pests, including cockroaches, spiders, flies, bugs, centipedes, and more.

24 Months after Sales Service of Pest Sticky Pads - If there is no glue on the edge of the pest glue board, please press the glue board before use. If you have any issues with the Mehani pest sticky board during the process, please let us know. Click “Add to Cart” now to keep Your home and Garden Healthy. Tips: Avoid direct sunlight and water exposure to maintain the stickiness of the glue trap. Also, be mindful of dust accumulation, which can affect adhesion.
